
@startuml
skinparam classAttributeFieldsUnderlined true

class Customer {
  -id: int
  -name: String
  -email: String
  -phoneNumber: String
}

class CarOwner {
  -id: int
  -name: String
  -contactInfo: String
  -carRegistrationNumber: String
}

class SelfDrivingCar {
  -id: int
  -licensePlate: String
  -model: String
  -status: String (Available/Busy/UnderMaintenance)
  -lastMaintenanceDate: Date
  -accidents: List<Accident>
}

class Accident {
  -id: int
  -date: Date
  -location: String
  -damageAmount: double
}

class RideService {
  -id: int
  -pickupTime: DateTime
  -dropoffTime: DateTime
  -pickupLocation: String
  -dropoffLocation: String
  -rideDuration: int
  -distance: double
  -fee: double
  -requestType: String (App/HandWave)
  -leadCustomer: Customer
}

class RideHailing extends RideService {
  -numPassengers: int (max 6)
}

class RideSharing extends RideService {
  -numPassengers: int (max 10)
  -customers: List<Customer>
  -negotiatedFeePerCustomer: double
  -treesPlanted: boolean
}

class SoberApp {
  -id: int
  -version: String
  -registeredUsers: List<Customer>
  -activeRequests: List<RideHailing>
}

class ImageRecognitionSystem {
  -id: int
  -accuracyRate: double
  -detectedRequests: List<RideHailing>
}

class SoberSystem {
  -id: int
  -registeredCarOwners: List<CarOwner>
  -registeredCars: List<SelfDrivingCar>
  -registeredCustomers: List<Customer>
  -totalRides: int
  -totalTreesPlanted: int
}

Customer "1" -- "0..*" RideHailing : uses
Customer "1" -- "0..*" RideSharing : participates in
RideHailing "1" -- "1" SelfDrivingCar : assigned to
RideSharing "1" -- "1" SelfDrivingCar : assigned to
SelfDrivingCar "1" -- "0..*" Accident : has
CarOwner "1" -- "1" SelfDrivingCar : owns
SoberApp "1" -- "1" ImageRecognitionSystem : integrates with
SoberSystem "1" -- "1" SoberApp : contains
SoberSystem "1" -- "1" ImageRecognitionSystem : contains
SoberSystem "1" -- "0..*" RideService : manages
SoberSystem "1" -- "0..*" Customer : manages
SoberSystem "1" -- "0..*" CarOwner : manages
SoberSystem "1" -- "0..*" SelfDrivingCar : manages
@enduml

### Explanation of Key Classes:
- **Customer**: Represents any user who can request a ride.
- **CarOwner**: A person who registers their car as a Sober cab.
- **SelfDrivingCar**: The vehicle used for either ride-hailing or ride-sharing.
- **Accident**: Tracks accidents involving a self-driving car.
- **RideService**: Base class for both `RideHailing` and `RideSharing`.
- **RideHailing**: A one-way, on-demand ride with up to 6 passengers.
- **RideSharing**: A shared ride with up to 10 passengers and negotiated pricing.
- **SoberApp**: The mobile application used by customers to hail cabs.
- **ImageRecognitionSystem**: Detects hand-waving gestures from users.
- **SoberSystem**: Central system that manages all operations, users, cars, and services.

